reviews.text: Food is only average, but the price is reasonable and service is good. Usually plenty of seats available.
The ambience is not that good but the food is alright.
Simple and decent food. Ambience a bit low light but covers up with food.

Food was great. However the portion sizes were unacceptable. 
The butter chicken only had 2 pieces of Chicken. Would have been nice to actually share it with my friends. But there wasn't enough... Probably won't come here enough.
Its expensive... food is good... ambiance is shaddy... at same food cost one can go to bombay dreams... whose ambience is really good
